{"word":"Ῥαμνοῦς","slug":"Ῥαμνοῦς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n92150\" key=\"*(ramnou=s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Ῥαμνοῦς</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">οῦντος</itype> (<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"var\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ contr.\">contr.</a></gram> </gramGrp> from <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ῥαμνόεις</foreign>), <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Rhamnus</title_>, a deme in Attica (named from the <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ῥάμνοι</foreign> growing in it), <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἡ ἐν Ῥ. θεός</foreign>, i.e. Nemesis, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0525.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:33:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Paus.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.33.2</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0099.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:1:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Str.\">Str.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.1.17</biblScope> </bibl> and <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0099.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ῥαμνοῦντι</foreign>, not <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐν Ῥ.</foreign>, <sense id=\"n92150.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">at Rhamnus</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0540.tlg019.perseus-grc1:28\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.28</biblScope></bibl>, etc.—Hence <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Ῥαμνούσιος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">α</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Rhamnusian</title_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0026.tlg001.perseus-grc1:157\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aeschin.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.157</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen> </sense> </entryFree>"}]}